Console Unfuddle, by Makarchev K.

create file HOME_DIR/.passwd_to_unfuddle with
subdomain 
login 
password 
default_projects

Tasks:
  un addcm NUMBER                      # add ticket comment
  un addt NUMBER HOURS COMMENT [DATE]  # add time
  un all [REGEXP]                      # show all tickets
  un assi TICKETS [NEW_ASSIGNEE]       # update tickets assingee
  un at PERIOD                         # show all times report for all projects
  un atm PERIOD                        # show my times report for all projects
  un clear                             # clear caches
  un help [TASK]                       # Describe available tasks or one specific task
  un my                                # show tickets assignee to me
  un new TITLE [ASSIGNEE] [PRIO]       # create ticket
  un projects                          # show all projects for your account
  un reports                           # show all reports for your account
  un show NUMBER [t]                   # show ticket by number, [t] - is option for show TimeEntries with ticket
  un t PERIOD                          # show all times report
  un test                              # test action
  un tm PERIOD                         # show my times report
  un upd TICKETS [NEW_STATUS]          # update tickets statuses

Used gems:
  unfuzzle by Patrick Reagan of Viget Labs
  grapt by Patrick Reagan
